text: Yuquan Temple or Jade Spring Temple may refer to these temples: *Yuquan Temple (Dangyang), Buddhist temple in Dangyang, Hubei, China *Yuquan Temple (Changsha), Buddhist temple in Changsha, Hunan, China ==See also== *Gyokusen- ji, Buddhist temple in Shimoda, Shizuoka Prefecture, Japan
title: Yuquan Temple
